== 爱国者广场 ==
[[File:Gillette_Stadium_Patriots_Home_Sign.JPG|left]]
在2006年，爱国者队和球队老板卡夫就宣布了一项投资计划，将在吉列体育场周围兴建“超级休闲娱乐中心”，并将之命名为“爱国者广场（Patriot Place）”<ref>{{english}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boston.com/sports/football/patriots/articles/2006/01/25/new_role_for_krafts_developers/|title=New role for Krafts: developers|work=[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]|first=Steve|last=Bailey|date=2006-01-25|accessdate=2009-07-08|archive-date=2012-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023210438/http://www.boston.com/sports/football/patriots/articles/2006/01/25/new_role_for_krafts_developers/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{english}}{{cite web |url=http://www.patriots.com/stadium/index.cfm?ac=stadiumnewsdetail&pid=18991&pcid=42 |title=Gillette Stadium: New for 2006 |work=Patriots.com |date=2006-04-02 |accessdate=2009-07-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070806113147/http://www.patriots.com/stadium/index.cfm?ac=stadiumnewsdetail&pid=18991&pcid=42 |archivedate=2007-08-06 }}</ref>。这项工程的预算高达三亿五千万美元，甚至要高于吉列体育场本身的建设费用。在当初购买福克斯堡体育场时，卡夫就已经购买了周边大约七百[[英亩|英亩]]的土地，而计划中的爱国者广场就坐落在这片土地上<ref name="Globe">{{english}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boston.com/sports/football/patriots/articles/2007/05/20/krafts_building_a_350m_patriot_place_complex_and_a_legacy/|title=Krafts building a $350m Patriot Place complex, and a legacy|work=[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]|first=Jenn|last=Abelson|date=2007-05-20|accessdate=2009-07-08|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065802/http://www.boston.com/sports/football/patriots/articles/2007/05/20/krafts_building_a_350m_patriot_place_complex_and_a_legacy/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

爱国者广场的一期工程於2007年底投入使用<ref>{{english}}{{cite web |url=http://wbztv.com/local/Bass.pro.Shops.2.605159.html |title=Bass Pro Shop Opens In Patriot Place |work=[[WBZ-TV|WBZ-TV]] |date=2007-11-15 |accessdate=2009-07-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080103163749/http://wbztv.com/local/Bass.pro.Shops.2.605159.html |archivedate=2008-01-03 }}</ref>，很多著名的销售商和卖场都在此时开始营业。2007年12月，爱国者和[[哥伦比亚广播公司|哥伦比亚广播公司]]宣布将共同开办主题餐厅和俱乐部，并将比赛的转播工作间设在其中。主题餐厅是二期工程的一部分，而二期工程的其他主要部分还包括一个购物广场，一个健身中心，一家电影院，一家四[[星级|星级]]酒店，爱国者球迷商店和一个与吉列体育场连在一起的纪念堂。纪念堂中包括一个两层楼的爱国者博物馆，用来展示球队的历史、回顾球队的辉煌<ref>{{english}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boston.com/sports/football/patriots/articles/2007/05/20/patriots_museum_will_have_pizzazz/|title=Patriots museum will have pizzazz|work=[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]|first=Keith|last=Reed|date=2007-05-20|accessdate=2009-07-08|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303201259/http://www.boston.com/sports/football/patriots/articles/2007/05/20/patriots_museum_will_have_pizzazz/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年7月到爱国者赛季开始前，购物广场，球迷商店，餐厅和纪念堂已经陆续开始接待游客，而剩余项目，包括酒店和健身中心也将于2009年正式对外开放。

